%% Diagram: One frame's scheduling across threads (cc::Scheduler state machine)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant V as Viz (display compositor)
    participant C as Compositor thread (cc::Scheduler)
    participant M as Main thread (Blink)
    participant W as Compositor workers / Viz raster

    V->>C: BeginFrame at VSync
    Note over C: BeginImplFrame
    C->>M: BeginMainFrame (BeginFrameArgs)
    Note over M: rAF, Animate, Style, Layout,<br/>Pre-paint, Scroll, Paint
    M-->>C: NotifyReadyToCommit (sync)
    Note over M: Main thread free for next frame
    C->>C: ScheduledActionCommit<br/>(copy property trees + display lists)
    C->>W: PrepareTiles / raster
    W-->>C: ReadyToActivate
    C->>C: ActivateSyncTree (pending becomes active)
    C->>V: Submit CompositorFrame
    V->>V: SurfaceAggregator combines frames
    V->>V: Draw to GPU at next VSync
